    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: 30 long lines.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in a maghribi in reddish ink; pointed.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Title page decoration of a larger rectangle with knotwork frame divided by another knotwork line with the basmallah above the line and the title in a circular medallion centered in the lower square (p. 1).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Origin: Composed and published in 1793, in Palermo, Italy.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
